cacheTempView(sql="
 select
          distinct so.orderId,so.subOrderId,afOrderId,to_date(from_unixTime(so.createdDate/1000)) as date,UNIX_TIMESTAMP(attributedTouchTime)*1000+19800000 as time,campaign,afAdset,mediaSource from `last180Days(appsflyerPurchase)` ap

          where (lower(mediaSource)  like '%google%') and lower(campaign) not like '%7d%'

union

          join `temp.a_11` 
          so on so.orderCode=ap.afOrderId and UNIX_TIMESTAMP(attributedTouchTime)*1000+19800000<createdDate

          where (lower(mediaSource)  like '%google%') and lower(campaign) like '%7d%'

","temp.c_11")

paragraphs.title: Base (AppsFlyer+SessionSummary 1 Day)
paragraphs.text:
cacheTempView(sql="
with
d as 
(
select distinct a.orderId,a.subOrderId,a.guid,a.date,b.utmSource, utmCampaign from `temp.a_11` a left join `temp.b_11` b on a.guid=b.guid and a.createdDate>b.time and a.createdDate<b.time+86400000 
where (lower(utmSource) like '%earth%'
			) and lower(utmCampaign) not like '%7d%'
			
			
union

select distinct a.orderId,a.subOrderId,a.guid,a.date,b.utmSource ,utmCampaign from `temp.a_11` a left join `temp.b_11` b on a.guid=b.guid and a.createdDate>b.time and a.createdDate<b.time+7*86400000 
where (lower(utmSource) like '%earth%'
			) and lower(utmCampaign) like '%7d%'

 )
 
 select distinct a.subOrderId,a.orderId,a.guid,deviceType,a.date,utmSource,mediaSource, utmCampaign,campaign,afAdset from  `temp.a_11` a left join  d on a.subOrderId=d.subOrderId left join `temp.c_11` c on c.subOrderId=a.subOrderId
 
 
         ","temp.base_n_11")
